  "prompt": "Where do you get the best cakes in pune?",
  "response": "Pune is known for its vibrant food scene, and there are several bakeries and patisseries that offer some of the best cakes in the city. Here are a few popular spots to get delicious cakes in Pune:\n\n1. **Kayani Bakery** (MG Road, Camp)  \n   - Known for its classic and timeless baked goods, Kayani Bakery offers cakes like plum cake, fruit cake, and other traditional favorites.  \n\n2. **German Bakery** (Koregaon Park)  \n   - A popular spot for cakes, pastries, and desserts, German Bakery has a cozy vibe and a good selection of baked treats.  \n\n3. **Theobroma** (Kothrud, Kalyani Nagar, Aundh, and other locations)  \n   - Famous for its rich and decadent cakes, Theobroma offers a variety of flavors, including red velvet, chocolate truffle, and more.  \n\n4. **La Folie Lab** (Kalyani Nagar)  \n   - A high-end patisserie, La Folie Lab is known for its artisanal cakes, macarons, and pastries. Their cakes are beautifully crafted and perfect for special occasions.  \n\n5. **Melveerra** (Baner, Kothrud, and other locations)  \n   - Offering a range of eggless and vegan cakes, Melveerra is a great choice for those with dietary restrictions. Their cakes are moist, flavorful, and beautifully decorated.  \n\n6. **Love & Cheesecake** (Kothrud, Baner, and other locations)  \n   - Known for its cheesecakes, this place also offers a variety of other cakes and desserts. Their cakes are rich, creamy, and perfect for indulging.  \n\n7. **Cakes of Joy** (Kalyani Nagar, Baner, and other locations)  \n   - Specializing in custom-designed cakes, Cakes of Joy offers a wide variety of flavors and themes for birthdays, anniversaries, and celebrations.  \n\n8. **Britannia & Co.** (FC Road)  \n   - Known for its quaint charm and classic baked goods, Britannia & Co. offers simple yet delicious cakes like chocolate cake and fruit cake.  \n\nThese are just a few of the many places in Pune where you can find amazing cakes. Depending on your preferences and location, you\u2019re sure to find something that suits your taste!",
  "temperature": 1.0,
